snippet.title: Tobe's VA - Nana
snippet.description:
Tobe's Vertical Adventure trailer for alternate character, Nana.

Unlike the XBLIG Version, player can now play the character as Nana. She can perform a double jump but lacks Tobe's agility. The different abilities also means different performance in the co-op mode, which player needs to work together to cover each other's strength and weakness.
